A pacman-liked script for Debian users

Query

  pacman -Q    -> dpkg --get-selections | grep install
  pacman -Qi   -> dpkg-query -s <foobar>
  pacman -Ql   -> dpkg-query -L <foobar>

Synchronize

  pacman -Ss   -> apt-cache search <foobar>
  pacman -Sy   -> apt-get update
  pacman -Su   -> apt-get upgrade
